com.patrickauth.petapp

Class Listing

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.patrickauth.petapp.Listing

  • public class Listing
extends java.lang.Object
    This class serves as the Model for Listings/Bookings posted by Pet Owners. The default constructor takes in the Listing's ID or the other constructor allows for a Listing object to be created by passing in all of the necessary parameters. Data from the PetPanion server about a listing can be fetched using getListing()
    Since:
    2020-12-16
    Version:
    1.1
    Author:
    Pat Auth, Conor O'Brien

      • Listing

        public Listing(int listingID)
        Default constructor for creating a listing with only the ID.

      • Listing

        public Listing(int listingID,
               int posterID,
               int petID,
               int sitterID,
               java.lang.String description,
               java.lang.String startDate,
               java.lang.String endDate,
               int active,
               double latitude,
               double longitude,
               int isSleepover)
        Expanded constructor for creating a listing with all of the Listing's expected and necessary parameters
        Parameters:
        listingID: - integer representing the ID of the listing in the system
        posterID: - integer representing account ID of the owner who made the listing
        petID: - integer representing the pet ID who belongs to the posterID
        sitterID: - integer of the account ID of the sitter who has accepted the listing, empty values are unfilled listings
        description: - the owner's description of the listing
        startDate: - the date the pet sitting services are requested to begin on by the owner
        endDate: - the date the pet sitting services are to finish by
        active: - indicates if the listing should be actively shown in the listings, or if hidden by the owner
        latitude: - latitude coordinate of the owner's address, or sitter's address if sleepover
        longitude: - longitude coordinate of the owner's address, or sitter's address if sleepover
        isSleepover: - integer representing a boolean value whether this listing is a sleepover or not
